OL,3,CHomeless men turned away from hotel in
OL,4,Csub-zero temperatures
OL,6,FTwo men were turned away by the
OL,7,FHoliday Inn Express on Oxford road -
OL,8,Feven though their booking was already
OL,9,Fpaid for. Credit: Instgram/@madd manneh
OL,11,FTwo homeless men were "inhumanely"
OL,12,Fturned away from a hotel as
OL,13,Ftemperatures plummeted to -6C,
OL,14,Fdespite a booking already being paid
OL,15,Ffor.
OL,17,FAmanda Thompson, from outreach group
OL,18,FTwo Brews, had used an online booking
OL,19,Fsite to secure two double rooms at a
OL,20,FHoliday Inn in Manchester for the men
OL,21,Fwho she supports.
