OL,3,CHomeless men turned away from hotel in
OL,4,Csub-zero temperatures
OL,6,FWith the sub-zero conditions outside,
OL,7,Fshe used donations and money from her
OL,8,Fown pocket for the booking to bring
OL,9,Fthem in out of the cold - but the men
OL,10,Fwere turned away at the door.
OL,12,FThe hotel chain has now said that
OL,13,Fdecision was "not in keeping with our
OL,14,Fpolicy" and that steps are being taken
OL,15,Fto "internally to strengthen our
OL,16,Ftraining."
