OL,3,CHomeless men turned away from hotel in
OL,4,Csub-zero temperatures
OL,6,FBut Amanda says the "inhumane"
OL,7,Ftreatment the men received from the
OL,8,Ffront desk of the hotel on Oxford Road
OL,9,Fin the city centre was "visual
OL,10,Fdiscrimination."
OL,12,FA member of staff on reception
OL,13,Fexplained to the men how they could
OL,14,Fnot honour the booking, which cost
OL,15,Fmore than #200.
