OL,3,CHomeless men turned away from hotel in
OL,4,Csub-zero temperatures
OL,6,FIn a video taken by an Instagram user,
OL,7,Fwho walked the two men to the hotel,
OL,8,Fthe member of staff on reception can
OL,9,Fbe heard saying: "Guys, I'm not going
OL,10,Fto lie to you, I'm not going to be
OL,11,Fable to check you in.
OL,13,F"Full truth and transparency, I know
OL,14,Fthat you're from the street and the
OL,15,Fhotel doesn't allow it.
OL,17,FThey added: "It's not a personal
OL,18,Fthing. We know people, I've been doing
OL,19,Fthe door for a long while. It's the
OL,20,Fcompany's policy. It's not mine
OL,21,Fpersonally, it's the company's."
