OL,3,CHomeless men turned away from hotel in
OL,4,Csub-zero temperatures
OL,6,FThe men were later booked into a
OL,7,Fnearby Travelodge, which accepted the
OL,8,Fbooking.
OL,10,FAmanda said: "It's disgusting. We then
OL,11,Fwent back to the Travelodge on Upper
OL,12,FBrook Street and they accepted them
OL,13,Fstraight away and were so helpful.
OL,15,F"We had six or seven people in there
OL,16,Fwho we supported on the Sunday night,
OL,17,Fand got four dogs in too.
