OL,3,CHomeless men turned away from hotel in
OL,4,Csub-zero temperatures
OL,6,F"I can't wrap my head around how you
OL,7,Fcan go to the desk, with a booking
OL,8,Fthat is paid for, and turned away just
OL,9,Ffor being a rough sleeper.
OL,11,F"They could've been hard working men
OL,12,Fand they have been judged on how they
OL,13,Flook. They just took one look at them
OL,14,Fand made the decision. It's inhumane."
OL,16,FAmanda Thompson from outreach group
OL,17,F'Two Brews' told ITV News the hotel
OL,18,Fhas apologised to the wrong person.
