OL,3,CHomeless men turned away from hotel in
OL,4,Csub-zero temperatures
OL,6,FHoliday Inn Express Manchester CC -
OL,7,FOxford Road spokesperson said: "After
OL,8,Fspeaking with team members, we
OL,9,Frecognise that this incident is not in
OL,10,Fkeeping with our policy of welcoming
OL,11,Fall and should have been handled
OL,12,Fdifferently.
OL,14,F"We sincerely apologise to the guests
OL,15,Faffected and are taking steps
OL,16,Finternally to strengthen our training."
OL,18,FThe incident comes just weeks after
OL,19,Fhomeless man Anthony Horn, 47, was
OL,20,Ffound dead on Boxing Day morning.
