OL,3,CHomeless men turned away from hotel in
OL,4,Csub-zero temperatures
OL,6,FIt is thought the dad may have died
OL,7,Ffrom the cold weather after he his
OL,8,Fbody was discovered in a tent next to
OL,9,Fa canal near the Bridgewater Hall in
OL,10,FManchester city centre.
OL,12,FIHG, which runs the Holiday Inn brand,
OL,13,Fstates online that it "offers access
OL,14,Ffor all" and that it "aims to make
OL,15,Fhotel facilities available and
OL,16,Faccessible to all guests equally",
OL,17,Fadding: "In rare instances where this
OL,18,Fis not possible, we will endeavour to
OL,19,Foffer a suitable alternative."
